/* ΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇ Component ΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇ */

export default function ProfileDashboard() {
  const { walletAddress, connectWallet, stellarPublicKey, isStellarConnected, connectStellar, fetchProfileAndTier } = useAuth();
  const { showError } = useError();
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  const location = useLocation();

  const account = isStellarConnected ? stellarPublicKey : walletAddress;
  const [userTier, setUserTier] = useState(0);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);
  const [saving, setSaving] = useState(false);
  const [isEditing, setIsEditing] = useState(false);
  const [hasProfile, setHasProfile] = useState(false);

  // Passkey smart account state
  const [isPasskeyActive, setIsPasskeyActive] = useState(() => {
    return localStorage.getItem('spectra_passkey_active') === 'true';
  });
  const [isRegisteringPasskey, setIsRegisteringPasskey] = useState(false);

  const [formData, setFormData] = useState({
    name: '',
    email: '',
    phone: '',
    bio: '',
    avatarId: 1
  });

  useEffect(() => {
    if (account) {
      loadProfile(account);
    } else {
      setHasProfile(false);
      setFormData({ name: '', email: '', phone: '', bio: '', avatarId: 1 });
      setUserTier(0);
    }
  }, [account, isStellarConnected]);

  const loadProfile = async (address) => {
    setLoading(true);
    try {
      if (isStellarConnected) {
        const [stellarProfile, tier] = await Promise.all([
          getProfile(address).catch(() => null),
          getUserTier(address).catch(() => 0),
        ]);

        if (stellarProfile && stellarProfile.name) {
          setHasProfile(true);
          setFormData({
            name: stellarProfile.name,
            email: stellarProfile.email,
            phone: stellarProfile.phone,
            bio: stellarProfile.bio,
            avatarId: stellarProfile.avatar_id || 1,
          });
        }
        setUserTier(Number(tier));
      } else {
        await ensureBaseSepolia();
        const provider = new ethers.BrowserProvider(window.ethereum);
        const contract = new ethers.Contract(CONTRACT_ADDRESSES.SPECTRA_PROFILE, CONTRACT_ABIS.SPECTRA_PROFILE, provider);

        try {
          const profile = await contract.getProfile(address);
          if (profile.exists) {
            setHasProfile(true);
            setFormData({
              name: profile.name,
              email: profile.email,
              phone: profile.phone,
              bio: profile.bio,
              avatarId: Number(profile.avatarId)
            });
          }
        } catch (e) {}

        try {
          const saasContract = new ethers.Contract(
            CONTRACT_ADDRESSES.SPECTRA_SAAS,
            CONTRACT_ABIS.SPECTRA_SAAS,
            provider
          );
          const tier = Number(await saasContract.getUserTier(address));
          setUserTier(tier);
        } catch (e) {}
      }
    } catch (err) {
      console.warn('Failed to load profile data:', err);
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const saveProfile = async () => {
    setSaving(true);
    try {
      if (isStellarConnected) {
        if (hasProfile) {
          await updateProfile(stellarPublicKey, formData);
        } else {
          await createProfile(stellarPublicKey, formData);
        }
        setHasProfile(true);
        setIsEditing(false);
        if (fetchProfileAndTier) await fetchProfileAndTier(stellarPublicKey, true);
      } else {
        await ensureBaseSepolia();
        const provider = new ethers.BrowserProvider(window.ethereum);
        const signer = await provider.getSigner();
        const contract = new ethers.Contract(CONTRACT_ADDRESSES.SPECTRA_PROFILE, CONTRACT_ABIS.SPECTRA_PROFILE, signer);

        let tx;
        if (hasProfile) {
          tx = await contract.updateProfile(formData.name, formData.email, formData.phone, formData.bio, formData.avatarId);
        } else {
          tx = await contract.createProfile(formData.name, formData.email, formData.phone, formData.bio, formData.avatarId);
        }
        await tx.wait();
        if (fetchProfileAndTier) await fetchProfileAndTier(walletAddress, false);
        setIsEditing(false);
      }
    } catch (err) {
      showError(err.message || 'Failed to save profile. Make sure to confirm transaction.');
    } finally {
      setSaving(false);
    }
  };

  // ΓöÇΓöÇ Passkey Smart Account Registration hook (Task 3) ΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇ
  // Ponytail: Native WebAuthn API handles registration biometric checks natively.
  const handleRegisterPasskey = async () => {
    if (!navigator.credentials) {
      showError('WebAuthn biometrics are not supported or available on this device.', 'Passkey Error');
      return;
    }

    setIsRegisteringPasskey(true);
    try {
      const challenge = crypto.getRandomValues(new Uint8Array(32));
      const userId = crypto.getRandomValues(new Uint8Array(16));

      const creationOptions = {
        publicKey: {
          challenge,
          rp: { name: "Spectra OS" },
          user: {
            id: userId,
            name: formData.email || "user@spectra.ai",
            displayName: formData.name || "Spectra Smart Account",
          },
          pubKeyCredParams: [
            { type: "public-key", alg: -7 } // ES256 (secp256r1) compatible with Stellar Protocol 27
          ],
          timeout: 60000,
          authenticatorSelection: {
            userVerification: "required",
            residentKey: "required"
          }
        }
      };

      console.log('[Passkey] Requesting biometric registration credentials...');
      const credential = await navigator.credentials.create(creationOptions);

      if (credential) {
        localStorage.setItem('spectra_passkey_active', 'true');
        setIsPasskeyActive(true);
        console.log('[Passkey] Smart account registered and backed by hardware enclave.');
      }
    } catch (err) {
      showError(err.message || 'Passkey registration cancelled.', 'Biometric Auth Failed');
    } finally {
      setIsRegisteringPasskey(false);
    }
  };

  // ΓöÇΓöÇ Dynamic Suggestions click-handler ΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇ
  const handleSuggestionClick = (actionText) => {
    if (actionText.includes('Mint Nexus')) {
      navigate('/mint');
    } else if (actionText.includes('Swap') || actionText.includes('route')) {
      navigate('/agent');
    }
  };

  const getTierName = () => {
    if (userTier === 0) return 'ALPHA';
    if (userTier === 1) return 'VECTOR';
    return 'NEXUS';
  };

  if (!account) {
    return (
      <Container className="flex items-center justify-center bg-grid">
        <GlassCard className="max-w-md w-full text-center" initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}>
          <Shield size={56} className="mx-auto mb-6 text-purple-500" />
          <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Web3 Identity Gateway</h1>
          <p className="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-8">
            Connect your wallet or register a passkey smart account to access your unified profile and bento analytics dashboard.
          </p>
          <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <ActionButton onClick={() => connectWallet().catch(() => {})}>
              Connect Ethereum Wallet
            </ActionButton>
            <SecondaryButton onClick={() => connectStellar().catch(() => {})}>
              Connect Stellar (Soroban Snap)
            </SecondaryButton>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>
      </Container>
    );
  }

  return (
    <Container className="bg-grid">
      {/* Bento Grid layout with responsive Tailwind Grid styling */}
      <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        {/* Column 1: Identity Card */}
        <GlassCard className="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-6">
          <div className="flex justify-between items-center">
            <GlowingBadge>Identity Node</GlowingBadge>
            {!isEditing && !loading && (
              <SecondaryButton onClick={() => setIsEditing(true)}>
                <Edit2 size={13} /> Edit Profile
              </SecondaryButton>
            )}
          </div>

          {isEditing ? (
            <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
              {/* Avatar Picker */}
              <div className="grid grid-cols-6 gap-3">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6].map(id => (
                  <button 
                    key={id}
                    className={`aspect-square rounded-xl overflow-hidden border-2 transition ${formData.avatarId === id ? 'border-purple-500' : 'border-transparent'}`}
                    onClick={() => setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, avatarId: id }))}
                  >
                    <img src={`/profile/${id}.png`} alt={`Avatar ${id}`} onError={(e) => { e.currentTarget.src = 'https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=' + id; }} />
                  </button>
                ))}
              </div>

              <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <Subtitle>Display Name</Subtitle>
                <Input placeholder="E.g. Hacker Neon" value={formData.name} onChange={e => setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, name: e.target.value }))} />
              </div>

              <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <Subtitle>Bio</Subtitle>
                <TextArea placeholder="Decentralized identity developer..." value={formData.bio} onChange={e => setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, bio: e.target.value }))} />
              </div>

              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <Subtitle>Email</Subtitle>
                  <Input type="email" placeholder="neon@spectra.ai" value={formData.email} onChange={e => setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, email: e.target.value }))} />
                </div>
                <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <Subtitle>Phone</Subtitle>
                  <Input placeholder="+1 555-0199" value={formData.phone} onChange={e => setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, phone: e.target.value }))} />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div className="flex gap-4 mt-4">
                <ActionButton onClick={saveProfile} disabled={saving}>
                  {saving ? 'Saving...' : <><Save size={16} /> Save Changes</>}
                </ActionButton>
                <SecondaryButton onClick={() => setIsEditing(false)}>Cancel</SecondaryButton>
              </div>
            </div>
          ) : (
            <div className="flex flex-col gap-6">
              <div className="flex items-center gap-6">
                <div className="w-24 h-24 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-purple-900 border-2 border-purple-500/30 flex-shrink-0">
                  <img src={`/profile/${formData.avatarId}.png`} alt="Profile Avatar" onError={(e) => { e.currentTarget.src = 'https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=' + formData.avatarId; }} />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold">{formData.name || 'Anonymous User'}</h1>
                  <span className="text-purple-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">{getTierName()} Subscriber</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p className="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                {formData.bio || 'No bio provided. Complete your profile node to register details.'}
              </p>

              <hr className="border-zinc-800" />

              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-zinc-300">
                  <Mail size={16} className="text-zinc-500" />
                  <span>{formData.email || 'No email registered'}</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-zinc-300">
                  <Phone size={16} className="text-zinc-500" />
                  <span>{formData.phone || 'No phone registered'}</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-zinc-300 md:col-span-2">
                  <Shield size={16} className="text-zinc-500" />
                  <span className="font-mono text-xs">{account}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          )}
        </GlassCard>

        {/* Column 2 / Row 1: Plan Status */}
        <GlassCard className="flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <Subtitle>SaaS Engine</Subtitle>
            <ValueLarge>{getTierName()}</ValueLarge>
            <p className="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-2 leading-relaxed">
              Tier governs your transaction quota limits and gasless sponsorship tier.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div className="mt-8 flex justify-between items-center">
            <span className="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-medium">Daily Limit: {userTier === 0 ? '20' : userTier === 1 ? '60' : '100'} txs</span>
            <Zap size={22} className="text-amber-500 animate-pulse" />
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        {/* Column 2 / Row 2: Passkey Smart Account Hub (Task 3) */}
        <GlassCard className="md:col-span-1 flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <Subtitle>Hardware Lock</Subtitle>
              {isPasskeyActive ? (
                <span className="text-[10px] bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold">ACTIVE</span>
              ) : (
                <span className="text-[10px] bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold">INACTIVE</span>
              )}
            </div>
            <ValueLarge>Passkey Hub</ValueLarge>
            <p className="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-2 leading-relaxed">
              Activate Passkey Smart Accounts for seed-phrase free biometric sign-offs on Stellar.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div className="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-4">
            {isPasskeyActive ? (
              <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-400">
                <CheckCircle size={14} /> Registered Biometric Key
              </div>
            ) : (
              <ActionButton onClick={handleRegisterPasskey} disabled={isRegisteringPasskey}>
                <Key size={14} /> {isRegisteringPasskey ? 'Registering...' : 'Register Passkey'}
              </ActionButton>
            )}
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        {/* Column 3: Dynamic Suggestions (Task 3) */}
        <GlassCard className="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <Subtitle>AI Recommendations</Subtitle>
          <div className="flex flex-col gap-3">
            {[
              'Mint Nexus Badge using XLM',
              'Find bridging route to Sepolia',
              'Settle SaaS x402 Micropayment',
              'Enable smart account limits'
            ].map(suggestion => (
              <SuggestionItem key={suggestion} onClick={() => handleSuggestionClick(suggestion)}>
                <SuggestionText>{suggestion}</SuggestionText>
                <ArrowRight size={13} className="text-zinc-500" />
              </SuggestionItem>
            ))}
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        {/* Column 3: SaaS x402 Micropayment log (Task 3) */}
        <GlassCard className="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div className="flex justify-between items-center">
            <Subtitle>SaaS Micropayment Activity Log (x402)</Subtitle>
            <Activity size={16} className="text-purple-500" />
          </div>
          <div className="overflow-x-auto w-full">
            <table className="w-full text-left text-xs border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr className="border-b border-zinc-800 text-zinc-500 font-semibold">
                  <th className="pb-3">Type</th>
                  <th className="pb-3">Token</th>
                  <th className="pb-3">Amount</th>
                  <th className="pb-3">Sponsor Proof (Stellar Tx Hash)</th>
                  <th className="pb-3">Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr className="border-b border-zinc-900 text-zinc-300">
                  <td className="py-3 font-semibold text-purple-400">x402 API Fee</td>
                  <td className="py-3 font-mono">USDC_SAC</td>
                  <td className="py-3">0.05 USDC</td>
                  <td className="py-3 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500">f87e5b...9a4c8d</td>
                  <td className="py-3"><span className="text-emerald-400">Settled</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr className="border-b border-zinc-900 text-zinc-300">
                  <td className="py-3 font-semibold text-purple-400">Badge Mint</td>
                  <td className="py-3 font-mono">XLM_SAC</td>
                  <td className="py-3">1.50 XLM</td>
                  <td className="py-3 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500">2d6a4f...7b1a2c</td>
                  <td className="py-3"><span className="text-emerald-400">Settled</span></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

      </div>
    </Container>
  );
}

import { defineConfig, loadEnv } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'

// https://vite.dev/config/
export default defineConfig(({ mode }) => {
  const env = loadEnv(mode, process.cwd(), '');
  return {
    plugins: [react()],
    assetsInclude: ['**/*.splinecode'],
    define: {
      'import.meta.env.VITE_ADMIN_URL': JSON.stringify(env.ADMIN_URL),
      'import.meta.env.VITE_ADMIN_PASS': JSON.stringify(env.ADMIN_PASS)
    },
    server: {
      proxy: {
        '/sarvam-api': {
          target: 'https://api.sarvam.ai',
          changeOrigin: true,
          rewrite: (path) => path.replace(/^\/sarvam-api/, ''),
        },
      },
    },
  }
})
